==English==

===Etymology===
From [[French]], from Old French, from the Old Italian ''cavalcata'' from ''cavalcare'', which meant to ride on horseback, from Medieval Latin ''caballicāre'', from the [[Latin]] ''caballus'', which means [[horse]].

